    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. it's a good start but a bit high-level. could you dive deeper into the \"national sovereignty\" aspect? specifically, how do proponents argue that uncontrolled borders fundamentally undermine the legal and social contract of a nation? help me make it sound really principled and philosophically grounded for the kids.",
